Introduction

Jung Taek Woon, popularly know as Leo, is the Main Vocalist of the Boy Group VIXX and its sub-unit VIXX L-R under Jellyfish Entertainment. Aside from his angelic voice, Leo is also known for his chic look and poker face.

On July 31, 2018 Leo debuted as a solo artist with the mini-album, "Canvas"
